---
title: All-American Chipotle-Glazed Beef Rump  with Potato Wedges & Tartare Slaw
description: Give beef rump a dash of flair with a glaze of chipotle sauce and sweet honey for a melding of robust flavours. Then, don’t stop
there. Ramp up your dish with a creamy tartare slaw tossed around with charred corn and peppery radish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
